@startuml
title 轉接器模式 (Adapter Pattern) - 電壓轉換系統

' --- 樣式設定 ---
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam class {
BackgroundColor White
ArrowColor #d35400
BorderColor #e67e22
}

' ==========================================
' 2. 物件轉接器模式 (Object Adapter)
' 使用組合 (Composition) 來連結 Adaptee
' ==========================================
package "物件轉接器 (Object Adapter)" {
class "Voltage220V" as O_Adaptee {
+ output220V(): int
}

interface "IVoltage5V" as O_Target {
    + {abstract} output5V(): int
}

class "VoltageAdapter" as O_Adapter {
    - voltage220V: Voltage220V
    + VoltageAdapter(v: Voltage220V)
    + output5V(): int
}

class "Phone" as O_Client {
    + charging(i: IVoltage5V): void
}

' 關係連線
O_Adapter o-- O_Adaptee : 組合 (Composition/Aggregation)
O_Adapter .up.|> O_Target : 實作 (Implementation)
O_Client ..> O_Target : 依賴 (Dependency)


}

' --- 說明註解 ---
note top of C_Adapter : 類別轉接器：\n透過繼承被轉接者類別，\n並實作目標介面。
note top of O_Adapter : 物件轉接器：\n持有被轉接者的實例 (Has-a)，\n比繼承更具彈性且符合合成複用原則。

@enduml